properties.Name: LearningEvent

Columns.Name: LearningEventId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Learning Event.

Columns.Name: LearningEventName
Columns.Description: The name of the Learning Event.

Columns.Name: LearningEventDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the Learning Event.

Columns.Name: LearningEventObjectivesStatement
Columns.Description:
A statement of the objectives to be achieved by the Learning Event.

The nature of this statement is typically applicable for including in a course catalog.

Columns.Name: StandardLearningEventFee
Columns.Description:
The standard fee in the associated currency for the Learning Event.

Courses offered at various locations have adjustments made based upon the cost of offering the Learning Event at that location based upon the Standard Learning Event Fee.

Columns.Name: CertificationExpirationPeriod
Columns.Description: The number of years that the Learning Event may be applied to the associated Curriculum before it must be retaken.

Columns.Name: RecommendedMinimumNumberAttendees
Columns.Description: The minimum number of attendees required to schedule and present the Learning Event.

Columns.Name: RecommendedMaximumNumberAttendees
Columns.Description: The maximum number of attendees allowed for the Learning Event.

Columns.Name: TargetNumberAttendees
Columns.Description: The target or optimum number of attendees for presentation of the Learning Event.

Columns.Name: PlannedMinimumLearningEventHourDuration
Columns.Description:
The planned minimum duration in hours in which the Learning Event can be presented.   

The number of hours will translate into some number of 'days' based upon the organizations work hours, training policy and staff decisions regarding optimum training schedules.

Columns.Name: PlannedMaximumLearningEventHourDuration
Columns.Description:
The planned maximum duration in hours in which the Learning Event can be presented.   

The number of hours will translate into some number of 'days' based upon the organizations work hours, training policy and staff decisions regarding optimum training schedules.

Columns.Name: TargetLearningEventHourDuration
Columns.Description:
The optimum duration in hours in which the Learning Event should be presented.   

The number of hours will translate into some number of 'days' based upon the organizations work hours, training policy and staff decisions regarding optimum training schedules.

Columns.Name: PlannedCostToProduceLearningEventPerLocation
Columns.Description: The target cost in currency to present the complete Learning Event at a location.

Columns.Name: PlannedCostToProduceLearningEventPerIndividual
Columns.Description: The target cost in currency to present the Learning Event per Individual at a standard location.

Columns.Name: LearningEventClassificationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Learning Event Classification.

Columns.Name: LearningEventOfferingStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Learning Event Offering Status.

Columns.Name: IsoLanguageId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an ISO Language.

Columns.Name: RegisteredDomainName
Columns.Description:
The registered domain name.

Ex:
    Domain name: www.example.net
    Registered domain name: example.net

Columns.Name: LearningEventTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Learning Event Type.

Columns.Name: ItemSku
Columns.Description: The Stock Keeping Unit identifier, which is typically used for inventory-related activities.
